{"tid":2126312,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深圳宣布收緊「跨境人士豁免隔離」","createTime":"2020-07-26T18:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T02:38:16.000Z","uid":362199,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13307863509383be03638b6ace1904a6ad622417","tid":2126312,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:05:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539476-20200723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539476-20200723.htm&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=99bce8e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539476-20200723.htm&h=72b84d34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539476-20200723.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳當局宣布，獲豁免隔離的香港跨境貨車司機，由香港經深港口岸入境時，必須持有粵港兩地政府認可的檢測機構，所發出72小時內核酸檢測陰性結果證明。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局副局長徐德義表示，已知悉要求，理解內地因應香港疫情轉變的新檢疫要求，特區政府關注新安排會否影響內地供港物流和食物供應，會與內地當局密切聯絡。"},{"pid":"ed8c44cd1b6590d53c585a3dbae1fdd0066e2972","tid":2126312,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:15:52.000Z","msg":"今次深圳都中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6c2bb3292c54f35abf31bb9df9a5a32754be75","tid":2126312,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:16:02.000Z","msg":"借位，睇下連登被沉底既熱門post:<br />\n<br />\n立場： 調查後發現中聯辦買入全棟樂怡軒同蒲飛路 18 號 並擁有選民登記<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAdhPNU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAdhPNU</a><br />\n<br />\n我係船員代理，有嘢想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118934</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》直擊上岸內地船員深水埗逛街 行高登豐澤7-11<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"ht